      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The blob moves up to its Speed and can move through the spaces of Huge or smaller creatures and objects. Teste de Resistência de Força: CD 23, cada criatura or object whose space the blob enters for the first time during this move. O alvo is engulfed. While engulfed, a target has Total Cover against attacks and other effects outside the blob, and when the blob moves, the engulfed target moves with it. A nonmagical object is destroyed after spending 1 minute engulfed.\nWhile engulfed, uma criatura takes 21 (6d6) dano de energia at the start of each of its turns, is suffocating, fica com a condição Impedido, and repeats the save at the end of each of its turns. An engulfed creature that is reduced to 0 Pontos de Vida dissolves into ash, which is ejected into the Astral Sea. O alvo escapes and enters the nearest unoccupied space.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
